    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.13.1"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">1</fw>
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                    <hi rend="caps">BENJAMIN DECASSERES
                
                        <hi rend="italic">
                        BOOKS BY
                            <lb/>
                        BENJAMIN DECASSERES:
                            <lb/>
                        THE SHADOW-EATER
                            <lb/>
                        CHAMELEON
                            <lb/>
                        MIRRORS OF NEW YORK
                            <lb/>
                        JAMES GIBBONS HUNEKER
                            <lb/>
                        <unclear>F</unclear>ORTY IMMORTALS
                            <lb/>
                        LITANIES OF NEGATION
                        ________
                            <lb/>
                        
                        THE MUSE OF LIES
                            <lb/>
                        BLACK SUNS
                            <lb/>
                        THE ETERNAL RETURN
                            <lb/>
                        THE EIGHTH HEAVEN
                            <lb/>
                        THE BOOK OF VENGEANCE  
                            <lb/>
                        SIR GALAHAD
                            <lb/>
                        BROKEN IMAGES
                            <lb/>
                        THE OVERLORD
                            <lb/>
                        SOMERSAULTS
                            <lb/>
                        WORDS, WORDS, WORDS
                            <lb/>
                        MARS AND THE MAN
                            <lb/>
                        THE COMEDY OF HAMLET
                        
                        BOOKS
                            <lb/>
                        DRAMA
                            <lb/>
                        MOTION PICTURES</hi>
                    </hi>
                </fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>Jan 1, 26 <note type="curatorial">[27]</note></dateline>
                
                    <salute>Dear Mr. Neihardt:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I appreciated your letter and also Mr. Johns'. You did the square thing. The <hi rend="underline">Post</hi> and Oppenheim refused to retract after repeated requests. They are therefore being sued in four suits for criminal and malicious libel. Their motives are unknown to me, they haven't even a toe to stand on, and if they book me for <del>any</del><add>an</add> easy mark, they've got another guess!</p>
                
                <p>My best wishes to you and Mr. Johns,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>Benjamin De Casseres</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <postscript>
                    <p>Will you please print the encolsed and send me several copies. I'm going to can this absurd charge.</p>
                </postscript>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
